description: This file defines the interface and exported APIs for a SNMP plugin module in a networking system. It includes function declarations for initialization, support checks, and memory diagnostics, along with relevant licensing and documentation comments.

methods.name: COSA_Init
methods.description: Initializes the plugin with maximum supported version and plugin info.

methods.name: COSA_Async_Init
methods.description: Performs asynchronous initialization of the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_IsObjectSupported
methods.description: Checks if a specified object is supported.

methods.name: COSA_Unload
methods.description: Unloads all created manager objects for the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_MemoryCheck
methods.description: Retrieves all memory details related to the plugin.

methods.name: COSA_MemoryTable
methods.description: Provides memory table information maintained by the plugin.
